abstract: National Beef said Tuesday it plans an initial public offering of its common shares, but the Kansas City, Mo.-based company has not yet set a price or disclosed how many it will sell.
snippet: National Beef said Tuesday it plans an initial public offering of its common shares, but the Kansas City, Mo.-based company has not yet set a price or disclosed how many it will sell.
lead_paragraph: National Beef said on Tuesday that it planned an initial public offering of its common shares, but the company, based in Kansas City, Mo., has not yet set a price or disclosed how many shares it will sell.

headline.main: National Beef Plans Initial Public Offering
